466
00:55:58,500 --> 00:56:00,500
Stav.

467
00:56:01,500 --> 00:56:03,300
Skini je.

468
00:56:07,200 --> 00:56:08,800
Stav.

469
00:56:08,700 --> 00:56:11,600
