00:56:15,800 --> 00:56:17,900
Bili ste u pravu.

472
00:56:21,700 --> 00:56:23,500
Dole.

473
00:56:23,500 --> 00:56:25,600
Zdravo!

474
00:56:25,500 --> 00:56:28,900
Mama.
